[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0533","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0533.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0321","title":"Sun Solaris kcms_configure 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 系统中的 kcms_configure 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于未对用户输入进行充分边界检查，本地攻击者可通过向该命令传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存数据并执行任意代码以获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 操作系统，需要本地用户权限方可利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0321"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-12-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Solaris 至 2.6 及以上版本，或安装 Sun 安全补丁 105401-01 (SPARC) / 105402-01 (x86)。如无法升级，移除 kcms_configure 的 setuid 位：chmod 0755 /usr/openwin/bin/kcms_configure 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0321","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19342","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0321.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0321","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0321.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0321.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j357-gv2q-h95j/GHSA-j357-gv2q-h95j.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0321.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0533.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0727","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0727.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0478","title":"HP-UX Sendmail 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 在处理连接请求时存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向运行 Sendmail 8.8.6 的 HP-UX 系统发送大量恶意连接请求，导致邮件服务耗尽系统资源而崩溃或无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 平台，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，无需认证即可远程触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0478"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-12-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.3 或更高版本。如无法升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中设置 MaxDaemonChildren 和 ConnectionRateThrottle 参数限制并发连接数以缓解拒绝服务攻击。具体补丁信息参见 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9904-097。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0478","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9904-097"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0727.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0148","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0148.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0057","title":"FreeBSD vacation 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统自带的 vacation 自动回复程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的电子邮件，触发 vacation 程序在自动回复时通过 sendmail 命令执行任意系统命令。该漏洞允许未经身份认证的远程攻击者在受影响系统上以邮件用户权限执行命令，危害等级高，CVSS 评分 7.5。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0057"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.587","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 3.2-RELEASE 或更高版本，该版本已修复 vacation 程序命令注入漏洞。如在受影响的 FreeBSD 3.x/4.0 系统上无法升级，可移除或禁用 vacation setuid 位（`chmod 755 /usr/bin/vacation`）并限制 sendmail 对 .forward 文件中 vacation 管道的调用权限。若业务上无需自动回复功能，直接卸载 vacation（`pkg_delete vacation`）或注释 .forward 中的 vacation 调用作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9811-087"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0148.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0141","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0141.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0052","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD IP碎片重组空指针解引用拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 和 OpenBSD 操作系统在处理 IP 分片重组时存在空指针解引用漏洞 (CWE-476)。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送精心构造的异常 IP 分片数据包，当内核试图对这些分片进行重组时会因空指针解引用导致系统崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 1.x/2.x、OpenBSD 2.2/2.3 及 BSD/OS 4.0 等多个版本，CVSS v3.1 评分 7.5，危害等级高。由于攻击无需任何特权且可远程触发，是早期 BSD 系统中影响广泛的拒绝服务漏洞之一。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0052"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.813","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.8 及以上版本，或 OpenBSD 至 2.4 及以上版本；在防火墙层面丢弃入站分片数据包（如 iptables -A INPUT -f -j DROP），或在内核中禁用 IP 分片重组功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/908","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1389"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0141.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0439","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0439.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0254","title":"HP OpenView SNMP 团体字符串信息泄露漏洞","description":"HP OpenView 存在隐藏的 SNMP 团体字符串漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用该默认团体字符串访问 SNMP 服务，进而读取或修改 MIB 表中的敏感配置信息，导致信息泄露或设备配置被篡改。受影响的系统包括 HP OpenView 网络管理软件，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0254"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.633","remediation":"升级 HP OpenView 至 NNM 7.53 或更高版本以修复此已知漏洞；立即修改所有 SNMP 团体字符串，禁止使用默认的 public/private 及已知隐藏字符串；在防火墙上限制仅允许受信任的管理主机访问 UDP 161 端口；如业务不需要 SNMP 功能，建议直接禁用 OpenView 的 SNMP 代理服务以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0254","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-239","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-239/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0254","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0254.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/c8b30957414aefbd6ba0b766db0d40593ba36fba/references/CVE-1999-0254-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p4hh-f88r-4p2r/GHSA-p4hh-f88r-4p2r.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest/blob/edcc863fa08f9024b1a3afc6f793747fed5f08ff/references/contrib1-CVE-1999-0254-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/snmp_default_communities.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0439.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0261","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0261.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0118","title":"IBM AIX 4.3 infod 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.3 系统的 infod 组件存在本地权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过 X display 机制向 infod 服务发送特制请求，利用该漏洞获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，成功利用后完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0118"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.630","remediation":"建议升级到 IBM AIX 4.3.3 及以上受支持版本，或安装对应 APAR 补丁 IX72357。如无需 infod 服务，可执行 `stopsrc -t infod` 停止该服务并通过注释 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中相关行禁用，以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91158980826979&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19287","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0118","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0118.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6c29fe92-c11f-40b7-bc14-92d730f9e4fc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0261.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0207","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0207.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0088","title":"IRIX 和 AIX automountd 服务远程代码执行漏洞","description":"IRIX 和 AIX 系统中的 automountd（autofsd）服务存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统的该服务发送特制请求，利用服务对输入参数过滤不严的缺陷，以 root 权限执行任意命令，完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响 IRIX 及 AIX 操作系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0088"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.370","remediation":"在 AIX 系统上执行 `stopsrc -g automountd` 禁用自动挂载服务，编辑 `/etc/rc.autofs` 注释自动启动项；在 IRIX 系统上执行 `/etc/init.d/autofs stop` 并删除 rc 链接。同时使用防火墙规则过滤 TCP/UDP 6969 端口，限制对 automountd 服务的网络访问。建议将老旧 IRIX/AIX 系统迁移至受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www-1.ibm.com/services/brs/brspwhub.nsf/advisories/852567CC004F9038852566BF007B6393/%24file/ERS-SVA-E01-1998_004_1.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0207.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0402","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0402.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0215","title":"SGI IRIX 和 OpenLinux routed 守护进程文件追加漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 3/4/5/6 及 OpenLinux 1.0/1.1 系统中运行的 routed 路由守护进程存在文件追加写入漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标系统的 routed 服务发送特制的 traceon 路由跟踪数据包，将任意数据追加到系统文件末尾，包括 /etc/passwd 等关键文件，进而实现权限提升或系统控制。该漏洞利用无需认证，远程即可触发，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0215"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-10-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.790","remediation":"建议禁用 routed 服务并改用静态路由或 gated 替代。如确需运行，升级到 IRIX 6.5.2+ 或 OpenLinux 1.1.2+ 版本，并在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 routed 条目后重启 inetd 服务以立即消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-012.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20805","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0215","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0215.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-45w3-m25h-r87g/GHSA-45w3-m25h-r87g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0215.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--580f5a91-46c0-44d8-8dec-8f18301e9dd8.json","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0402.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0143","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0143.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0053","title":"FreeBSD TCP RST 数据包拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 6.2 的 TCP 协议栈存在 TCP RST 包拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过伪造 TCP RST 数据包向已建立的 TCP 连接发送，导致目标系统上的合法 TCP 连接被异常中断。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，可造成受影响服务的可用性下降，影响范围包括运行 FreeBSD 6.2 的系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0053"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.047","remediation":"升级至 FreeBSD 7.0-RELEASE 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 FreeBSD 6.3-STABLE 分支的 tcp_input.c 补丁中修复。若无法升级，可在 pf 防火墙上添加规则限制每秒入站 RST 包数量：`pass in proto tcp flags R/R` 结合 `max-packets 100/sec` 作为临时缓解。同时建议在系统层面启用 syncookies（sysctl net.inet.tcp.syncookies=1）以降低 RST 欺骗影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6094"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0143.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0003","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0002","title":"Linux NFS mountd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NFS mountd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获取受影响系统的 root 权限。该漏洞主要影响 Linux 系统，包括 RedHat Linux 5.1 及 Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 等版本。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，建议立即升级至修复版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0002"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-10-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.113","remediation":"RedHat Linux 5.1 用户应升级至 RedHat Linux 5.2 或安装对应安全补丁；Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 用户需更新至修复版本；SGI 系统应安装公告 19981006-01-I 提供的补丁。在不影响业务的前提下，可禁用 NFS 服务（/etc/init.d/nfs stop）或使用 tcpwrappers（/etc/hosts.allow）限制对 rpc.mountd 的访问来源，同时通过防火墙仅允许可信 IP 访问 RPC 端口（111/TCP/UDP）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-006.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/121","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19096","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0002.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0002.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0002","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0002.json","https://github.com/demisto/content/blob/710308a4be78e89bc993b4d594b444aeb805b7d8/Packs/IntSight/Integrations/Rapid7ThreatCommand/README.md","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0002.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-222m-mgc9-9mqv/GHSA-222m-mgc9-9mqv.json","https://github.com/MAECProject/python-maec/blob/13e66105c9646156060d0896a4d54970ea358f44/maec/bindings/maec_bundle.py","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/FIRSTdotorg/Vuln4Cast/blob/c93910d268aa5b5d2260adb9b5d92094b2d06daf/YearlyVuln4Cast-V1.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0005","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0002","title":"Caldera OpenLinux NFS mountd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NFS 服务中的 mountd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获得 root 权限，实现完全控制目标系统。该漏洞主要影响 RedHat Linux 5.1、Caldera OpenLinux Standard 1.2 等 Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0002"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-10-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.113","remediation":"立即升级 NFS mountd 相关软件包。Red Hat Linux 用户应升级至 5.2 及以上版本；Caldera OpenLinux 用户应升级至 Standard 1.3 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上封锁 NFS 相关端口（如 TCP/UDP 111、2049），或直接禁用 NFS 服务（`/etc/init.d/nfs stop`）及 rpc.mountd 守护进程。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-006.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/121","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19096"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0562","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0562.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0343","title":"The Palace 客户端远程代码执行漏洞","description":"The Palace 是一款图形化在线聊天软件，其客户端存在远程代码执行漏洞。恶意 Palace 服务器管理员可通过向连接的客户端发送特制的指令数据包，诱使客户端执行任意系统命令或程序。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，受害者仅需连接至受控服务器即可触发。该漏洞影响全部 Palace 客户端版本，可导致客户端被完全控制。目前该软件已停止维护，无官方补丁提供。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0343"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-10-02","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"The Palace 客户端软件已于 2000 年代初停止维护，官方未发布任何安全补丁。建议立即停用该软件，迁移至 Signal、Matrix 等仍在维护的即时通讯方案。如确需继续使用，务必在隔离沙箱环境中运行客户端，仅连接可信服务器，并以最小权限账户执行，避免连接不受控的 Palace 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0343","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0343.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0343","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0343.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0343.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g4rh-vxc3-fpmr/GHSA-g4rh-vxc3-fpmr.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0343.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82274/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0343.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0562.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0369","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0369.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0186","title":"Sun Solaris SNMP 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统 SNMP 子代理程序存在默认团体字符串（community string）漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 SNMP 协议访问目标系统，利用该默认字符串执行任意命令获取 root 权限，或修改系统关键参数。此漏洞影响 Solaris 操作系统多个版本，攻击门槛低且危害极高，CVSS 评分 10.0，属于严重级别。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0186"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:47.033","remediation":"立即修改 SNMP 默认 community string，将 snmpd.conf 中默认的 \"public\" 改为自定义复杂字符串；升级 Solaris 至包含补丁 105230-xx (Solaris 2.5/2.5.1) 或 105231-xx (Solaris 2.4) 及更高版本；如无需 SNMP 子代理功能，禁用 snmpdx 守护进程；在防火墙层面限制 UDP 161 端口仅对可信管理站开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.novell.com/cgi-bin/search/searchtid.cgi?/10080762.htm","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-238/"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0369.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0760","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0760.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0506","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 域用户及管理员账户默认空密码漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 系统中，域用户或管理员账户存在默认空密码或未设置密码的安全缺陷。攻击者可利用该漏洞直接使用空白密码登录目标系统，获得未经授权的访问权限，进而完全控制受影响的服务器或工作站。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 版本，无需额外认证条件，危害等级高。建议管理员及时为所有账户设置强密码以修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0506"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.433","remediation":"立即为所有 Windows NT/2000 域用户和管理员帐户设置非空强密码，通过「域安全策略」启用「密码必须满足复杂性要求」并设置最短密码长度≥8 位，定期使用 `net user` 命令或专用工具扫描域中所有存在空密码/默认密码的帐户并强制修改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0506"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0760.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0810","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0810.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0546","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 来宾账户未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 操作系统默认启用了 Guest（来宾）账户，且该账户通常未设置密码或仅使用弱口令。本地或远程攻击者可通过 Guest 账户以空密码或弱口令登录目标系统，获得有限的系统访问权限，进而通过提权操作获取更高权限甚至完全控制目标系统。此漏洞影响所有 Windows NT 系列版本，属于典型的安全配置缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0546"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.500","remediation":"建议在 Windows NT 中通过「用户管理器」或 `net user guest /active:no` 命令禁用 Guest 账户；或为 Guest 账户设置复杂密码并移除 Administrators 等特权组成员身份。若业务不需要访客访问，应彻底禁用该账户。同时通过组策略限制本地登录权限作为纵深防御措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0546"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0810.toml"}]